item.title: Dom
item.description: Born in Providence, Rhode Island (U.S.A.) in 1996, Dominique Northecide is a full-stack developer and designer. After earning a BFA with a concentration in Graphic Design from Florida Atlantic University in Boca Raton, he obtained a master’s degree in UX/UI Design from the Rhode Island School of Design . It was at the RISD where Northecide was introduced to a curriculum established by Mies van der Rohe, formed from the notions of Bauhaus, that taught him to combine the fields of art, craft and design.
